.@Mike_Pence will do a fantastic job against left-wing Kamala Harris tonight at the #VPdebate 

He understands the American People treasure our Constitutional rights, our front line police, and tax cuts for all Americans 🇺🇸 

@realDonaldTrump and @VP are the team for THE PEOPLE! https://t.co/mYZvtHnIxV

COVID-19 was unleashed onto the world by China. 
 
@SpeakerPelosi now sides with Communist China by calling it the "Trump Virus."

Nancy, we’re both old enough to know what I mean when I say you’ve officially “jumped the shark.”

Our law enforcement community deserves our support &amp; the best training possible. 

Defunding the police is absolutely the wrong thing to do. I will never support it.

@realDonaldTrump’s Executive Order on Safe Policing for Safe Communities is the right thing to do.

I was proud to join my Indiana House colleagues to honor Sen. Richard Lugar, who will be remembered as one of America's greatest senators.

Nice words from @RepLarryBucshon. Godspeed, Senator. 🇺🇸

